    section.main-content-wrap.flex
      .main-content-box
        article.main-content.flex.flex-center
          .main-comment
            h1 Banking account for young people of all ages
            p Easy to open. Fun and secure to use. In your mobile.
          .main-btn
            a.fade-bg(href='#') Join for free
        article.main-content-img
          .main-img
            p.main-img-comment.font-smooth #DoYourThing
    section.interview-wrap
      .interview-box
        .interview-img
          img(src='images/indrek_neivelt-96x96.jpg', alt='circle-img')
        p.interview-cnt.font-smooth
          | &quot;We believe that banking in the future will be significantly different than we are used to. We imagine an amazing mobile experience that&rsquo;s user-friendly, engaging and priced in a fair way. Today, Pocopay is proud to give our customers such an experience.&quot;
        h2.interview-ipm Indrek Neivelt, CEO of Pocopay
    section.download-wrap
      article.download-box.clearfix
        .download
          img(src='images/pcpay-icon.jpg', alt='poco-icon')
          h1 Download Pocopay now
        .download-btn
          a(href='#')
            img.appstore-btn(src='images/App-Store-Logo.png', alt='appstore-btn')
          |  
          a(href='')
            img.playstore-btn(src='images/GooglePlay_logo.png', alt='playstore-btn')
    section.imformation-wrap.clearfix
      article.imformation-box.clearfix
        .imformation-part1.clearfix
          .frame
            img(src='images/iphone-frame.png', alt='ipone-frame')
          .frame-hover
            .frame-hover-wrap
              h3 Pay and request money instantly
              p
                | Make payments and money requests to telephone numbers and email addresses. Yes, the good old IBAN works too.
              |  
              a(href='#') View more
        .imformation-part2.clearfix
          .frame
            img(src='images/card_final_rgb.svg', alt='card-frame')
          .frame-hover
            .frame-hover-wrap
              h3 Contactless MasterCard debit card
              p
                | All Pocopay banking account users can order a Pocopay debit MasterCard straight from the app with one click. You can pay for your online and offline purchases with it.
              |  
              a(href='#') View more
    section.card-wrap.clearfix
      article.card-box.clearfix
        h2 Pocopay gives Apollo gift cards
        .card.clearfix
          .white-card.clearfix
            img.mb(src='Asset/icon__promocode_invite.svg', alt='white-card')
            p
              | Open free Pocopay account with promotion code &quot;Poco&quot; and get 5&euro; Apollo gift card.
          .blue-card.clearfix
            img.mb(src='Asset/icon__promocode_poco.svg', alt='blue-card')
            p
              | Invite your friends and family to Pocopay! They will get a 5&euro; Apollo gift card and so will you.
